SubDir HAIKU_TOP 3rdparty artpaint ;

SubInclude HAIKU_TOP 3rdparty artpaint artpaint ;
SubInclude HAIKU_TOP 3rdparty artpaint addons ;

AddFilesToHaikuImage apps artpaint : ArtPaint ;

AddFilesToHaikuImage apps artpaint add-ons : AHE.so ;
